import React from 'react'
import "../App.css"
import InvoiceUI from '../components/InvoiceUI'


const InvoiceNum=()=>{
    let invoicenum=document.getElementById("invoicenum").value
    let invoicedate=document.getElementById("invoicedate").value
    let invoicedue=document.getElementById("invoicedue").value
    let suppliername=document.getElementById("suppliername").value
    let supplieraddress=document.getElementById("supplieraddress").value
    let clientname=document.getElementById("clientname").value
    let clientaddress=document.getElementById("clientaddress").value

    console.log("Invoice Number:-"+invoicenum)
    console.log("Invoice Date:-"+invoicedate)
    console.log("Invoice Due Date:-"+invoicedue)
    console.log("Supplier Name:-"+suppliername)
    console.log("Supplier Address:-"+supplieraddress)
    console.log("Client Name:-"+clientname)
    console.log("Client Address:-"+clientaddress)

    }

function Invoice() {


    
    return (
        <>
           <InvoiceUI/>


        </>
    )
}

export default Invoice
export{InvoiceNum}
